c: 24
v: 21
t: "“E inu amene mwakhulupiliira! Musatsatire mapazi a satana. Ndipo amene atsatire mapazi a satana (asokera) ndithudi iye akulamula zauve ndi zoipa. Ndipo pakadapanda ubwino wa Allah ndi chifundo Chake pa inu, sakadayera aliyense mwa inu mpaka kalekale. Koma Allah amamuyeretsa amene wamfuna. Ndipo Allah Ngwakumva zonse; Wodziwa kwambiri"